OL,3,CMan who waved prosthetic leg at
OL,4,Cprotestors among four jailed after
OL,5,CPlymouth riot
OL,7,FFour men have been jailed for a total
OL,8,Fof more than seven years for their
OL,9,Fpart in the violent demonstrations in
OL,10,FPlymouth city centre on Monday 5
OL,11,FAugust.
OL,13,FAll four defendants appeared at
OL,14,FPlymouth Crown Court on Tuesday 13
OL,15,FAugust for sentencing having pleaded
OL,16,Fguilty to violent disorder at earlier
OL,17,Fhearings.
