OL,3,CMan who waved prosthetic leg at
OL,4,Cprotestors among four jailed after
OL,5,CPlymouth riot
OL,7,FDuring the violence, rocks and bottles
OL,8,Fwere thrown, police were injured and
OL,9,Fseveral members of the public were
OL,10,Fhurt.
OL,12,FJohn Cann, 51 from Patna Place,
OL,13,FPlymouth, was sentenced to three years
OL,14,Fin jail.
OL,16,FHe was caught on camera waving his
OL,17,Fprosthetic leg at opposing protestors
OL,18,Fduring the violence.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
