OL,5,CPlymouth riot
OL,7,FThe court was shown footage of Cann
OL,8,Flaunching a firework or flare towards
OL,9,Fthe counter-protesters before falling
OL,10,Foff his mobility aide.
OL,12,FThe police bodycam footage also showed
OL,13,FCann bending down to pick up an object
OL,14,Ffrom the floor before throwing it at
OL,15,Fthe opposing protestors.
OL,17,FCann asked a police officer if tax
OL,18,Fpayer money could be better spent
OL,19,Felsewhere rather than protecting
OL,20,F"these people", when referring to
OL,21,Fimmigrants.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
