OL,5,CPlymouth riot
OL,7,FThe court heard that Cann told police
OL,8,Fhe thought the protest would "kick
OL,9,Foff" because "an immigrant had killed
OL,10,Fsome girls" but insisted he was not
OL,11,Fracist.
OL,13,FWhile sentencing him for violent
OL,14,Fdisorder, Judge Robert Linford listed
OL,15,Fa long list of his previous
OL,16,Fconvictions and said he'd cost
OL,17,Ftaxpayers in the form of 357 months -
OL,18,Fnearly 30 years - in prison.
