OL,7,FThe judge told him "you have no right
OL,8,Fwhatsoever to say who should or should
OL,9,Fnot be in this country".
OL,11,FRyan Bailey, 41 of George Place,
OL,12,FPlymouth was handed 30 months behind
OL,13,Fbars.
OL,15,FBailey threw a missile at protesters
OL,16,Fon what the court described as the
OL,17,F"anti-fascism" side of the road and
OL,18,Fwas seen to join in with racist
OL,19,Fchanting.
