OL,7,FHe was heard shouting: "Immigrants not
OL,8,Fwelcome here".
OL,10,FGary Harkness, 51, from North Road
OL,11,FWest, Plymouth, was sentenced to 12
OL,12,Fmonths in jail.
OL,14,FHe was described as being "prolific"
OL,15,Fthroughout the evening and on numerous
OL,16,Foccasions was captured on CCTV or
OL,17,Fbodyworn cameras "front and centre" as
OL,18,Fpolice attempted to push crowds back.
OL,20,FHe was abusive towards officers and
OL,21,Fmade a threat of violence.
