OL,7,FHowever, Harkness was described by
OL,8,FJudge Robert Linford as being the
OL,9,F"least involved" in terms of "direct
OL,10,Fviolence" to come before him.
OL,12,FHanding out his sentence, Judge
OL,13,FLinford said: "Of the people I have
OL,14,Fthus far sentenced you are the person
OL,15,Fwho provides me with the most
OL,16,Fdifficulty because it cannot be
OL,17,Flevelled at you that you hit anyone,
OL,18,Fneither have you thrown anything,
OL,19,Fneither is it said that you spat at
OL,20,Fanybody.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@PO]qD@^OUrD@IO]uD@OOU
