OL,7,F"But it is accepted by you that you
OL,8,Fwere a party to this disorder and I
OL,9,Fhave to sentence you on the basis, and
OL,10,Fyou also know that anyone party to it
OL,11,Fhas to receive a custodial sentence."
OL,13,FHe added: "On August 5 this city was
OL,14,Fblighted by widespread disorder that
OL,15,Fwas centred on the Royal Parade `
OL,16,Fthere was one faction on one side and
OL,17,Fone faction on the other.
