OL,7,F"You didn't attend this evening, I'm
OL,8,Fsatisfied, with the intention of
OL,9,Fstarting or being involved in any
OL,10,Ftrouble.
OL,12,F"You didn't align yourself with either
OL,13,Ffaction, but you became involved and
OL,14,Fas a consequence of that you have now
OL,15,Fpleaded guilty to violent disorder.
OL,17,F"Your plea accepts that you threatened
OL,18,Funlawful violence and your conduct
OL,19,Fcould lead people to fear for their
OL,20,Fsafety."
