OL,7,FHarkness, who admitted having drunk
OL,8,Fheavily that day, was seen making lewd
OL,9,Fgestures and swearing during the
OL,10,Fevening and at another point pushes or
OL,11,Fis pushed by a police officer.
OL,13,FAt one point in the hearing, after
OL,14,Fwatching body-worn camera footage from
OL,15,Fthe event, the judge halted the
OL,16,Fhearing, seemingly frustrated that
OL,17,FHarkness was before him.
OL,19,FThe case was adjourned while the judge
OL,20,Fspoke to the prosecution's Lewis
OL,21,FAldous.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/16
