OL,7,FFollowing the adjournment Mr Aldous
OL,8,Ftold the court that Harkness had
OL,9,Feffectively encouraged the disorder.
OL,11,FAmer Walid, 24, of Central Park
OL,12,FTowers, who was a counter-protestor
OL,13,Fwas sentenced to 20 months behind bars.
OL,15,FWalid was seen throwing cans on four
OL,16,Foccasions back at the far-right side
OL,17,Fof the protest.
OL,19,FHis defence said he went not expecting
OL,20,Fviolence but solidarity with his
OL,21,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/16
