OL,7,FHe claimed he reacted after a bottle
OL,8,For can of alcohol was thrown at him.
OL,9,FHe said that he doesn't drink and was
OL,10,Foffended by this and became angry,
OL,11,Fthrowing other missiles at opposing
OL,12,Fprotesters.
OL,14,FThe court was told he shouted Allah
OL,15,FAkbar, in support of his religion
OL,16,Fagainst the racist slurs being chanted
OL,17,Fby the other side.
OL,19,FWalid could be seen surrounded by
OL,20,Fplacards saying "Love not hate".
