OL,7,FAll of the defendants except for Walid
OL,8,Fhad previous convictions recorded
OL,9,Fagainst them.
OL,11,FThe judge described last Mondays riots
OL,12,Fas a terrible incident where people
OL,13,Fran amok, intent on damaging property,
OL,14,Fharming others and intent on clashing
OL,15,Fwith anybody, including the police,
OL,16,Fwho disagreed with their views.
OL,18,FJudge Linford said that events on the
OL,19,Fevening of 5 August "caused serious
OL,20,Ffear in the community", as well as
OL,21,F"enormous disruption".
