OL,7,FHe said: "On the evening of 5 August
OL,8,Fthere was widespread public disorder
OL,9,Fin this city. The police attended in
OL,10,Fforce and acted with extraordinary and
OL,11,Fcommendable restraint.
OL,13,F"People ran amok throwing stones,
OL,14,Ffireworks and other missiles intent
OL,15,Fupon damaging property and harming
OL,16,Fothers.
OL,18,F"Word must go out that people who
OL,19,Fbehave in this way will go to prison
OL,20,Fand will be going to prison for a
OL,21,Fconsiderable period of time."
